  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located across the road to the Funicular and new Symphony gondola, La Toviere has unparalleled access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Espace Killy Ski Area">Espace Killy</a> resort. The hotel has a cosy and modern setting with contemporary furnishings. The 29 rooms are decorated in warm and relaxing tones, each with balcony and views of the valley. Dinner is available to pre-book at the hotelier's nearby restaurant - La Brasserie Louis or take advantage of the excellent bus links (5 mins) into Val d'Isere to enjoy a wide range of restaurants. The Tapas bar and lounge is a great space to unwind and enjoy a drink in front of two fireplaces, plus the hotel also offers excellent spa facilities. Unwind in the heated pool or whirlpool, purify yourself in the sauna &amp; steam room or indulge in a luxury face or body treatment created with 100% organic ingredients.</p>]]></description>
