  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have double or twin beds (please specify your preference when booking), WC, bath with shower head attachment, cable / satellite flat screen TV with English speaking channels, telephone, safe, towels, tea and coffee making facilities, mini bar, hairdryer, and all have balconies with surrounding mountain views.</p>
<ul>
<li>Classic rooms (A2) have a bath or shower. Sole occupancy (F1) is available at a supplement.</li>
<li>Larger Comfort rooms (B2) have a bath and shower and small lounge area.</li>
<li>Family Comfort rooms (C4) have a master bedroom, lounge area and bunk beds for children plus bath and shower.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
